sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Operator as Operator
    participant Browser as Dashboard
    participant Auth as Backend /auth
    participant Store as PostgreSQL

    Operator->>Browser: Open login page and submit credentials
    Browser->>Auth: POST /auth/token
    Auth->>Store: Load user and verify password hash
    Store-->>Auth: User record and org context
    Auth-->>Browser: JWT access token + profile payload
    Browser->>Browser: Persist token in cookie and localStorage
    Browser-->>Operator: Redirect into protected dashboard routes
